36:24.660 --> 36:27.663
BECAUSE HIS SYSTEM WAS TOO WEAK
TO FIGHT OFF THE FLU.

36:27.663 --> 36:31.014
BUT WHEN FERNANDA GOT SICK,
SHE STARTED TO DO SOME DIGGING.

36:31.014 --> 36:35.323
YOU CAN'T TIE ANY OF THAT
TO US.A SIMPLE BLOOD TEST WILL SHOW
JUST WHAT ADDITIVES

36:35.323 --> 36:37.282
WERE PRESENT IN HIS SYSTEM.
EVERYONE AT THE SHELTER CAN

36:37.282 --> 36:38.848
CONFIRM DRINKING THE SODAS.

36:38.848 --> 36:41.634
WHO GAVE THEM OUT
CAN BE TESTED AS WELL.

36:41.634 --> 36:47.466
ESTHER SAID THE SODA WAS
LOSING TOO MUCH FLAVOR

36:47.466 --> 36:50.295
SO WE STARTED USING GLYCOL
AS A STABILIZER.

36:50.295 --> 36:52.297
WE GOT A BAD BATCH.

36:52.297 --> 36:54.168
HOW BAD?

36:54.168 --> 36:57.171
ESTHER SAID YOU HAD TO DRINK
A LOT OF IT

36:57.171 --> 36:59.521
IN ORDER FOR THERE TO BE
ANY BAD EFFECTS.

36:59.521 --> 37:01.523
MOST PEOPLE JUST GOT
AN UPSET STOMACH.

37:01.523 --> 37:03.917
IT WAS ONLY LIKE
500 BOTTLES.

37:03.917 --> 37:07.442
YOU KNEW YOU WERE ENDANGERING
THE LIVES OF YOUR CONSUMERS.

37:07.442 --> 37:12.360
ESTHER SAID PULLING
THE PRODUCT WAS TOO EXPENSIVE

37:12.360 --> 37:15.189
AND KEPT SAYING
IT WAS NO BIG DEAL.

37:15.189 --> 37:17.670
WHO DRINKS 12 BOTTLES
IN ONE GO ANYWAY?

37:17.670 --> 37:21.674
RIGHT, AND THEN
THE HOMELESS MAN, MARTY, DIED.

37:21.674 --> 37:24.633
FERNANDA MADE THE CONNECTION,
STARTED ASKING QUESTIONS.

37:27.767 --> 37:30.378
FERNANDA WOULDN'T
LET IT GO,

37:30.378 --> 37:33.338
SAID WE HAD TO ISSUE
A MASSIVE RECALL.

37:33.338 --> 37:35.209
SHE'D TELL IF WE DIDN'T.

37:35.209 --> 37:37.603
AND THEN YOU KILLED
YOUR OWN COUSIN.

37:41.998 --> 37:43.783
[crying]

37:43.783 --> 37:46.089
YEAH, WE DID.

37:48.048 --> 37:49.441
[continues crying]

37:49.441 --> 37:52.052
AND THEN VALERIE SHOWED UP
A WEEK LATER,

37:52.052 --> 37:54.359
AND YOU KNEW
WHAT YOU HAD TO DO.

37:54.359 --> 37:56.535
[sniffles]

37:56.535 --> 38:00.582
I TOLD ESTHER. THAT LADY
DIDN'T KNOW ANYTHING.

38:00.582 --> 38:03.585
[sniffles] BUT SHE KEPT
SAYING SOMEONE LIKE HER

38:03.585 --> 38:07.589
WOULDN'T STOP COMING AROUND
AND ASKING QUESTIONS.

38:07.589 --> 38:11.158
[sighs] SO SHE HAD TO GO.

38:11.158 --> 38:12.768
[crying]

38:12.768 --> 38:15.467
[Nilda]
FERNANDA WAS MY PRIMA.

38:15.467 --> 38:19.384
SHE WAS SUPPOSED TO STICK UP
FOR HER OWN.

38:19.384 --> 38:21.342
BUT SHE CHOSE
THAT BITCH ON THE BUS

38:21.342 --> 38:23.736
OVER HER FAMILY.

38:23.736 --> 38:26.521
[continues crying]

38:34.747 --> 38:36.096
[zips bag]

38:53.505 --> 38:55.158
[sighs]

38:55.158 --> 38:59.075
THANK YOU, MAN.
I APPRECIATE IT. REALLY.

38:59.075 --> 39:00.468
IT'S JUST SODA.

39:00.468 --> 39:02.078
IT'S DIET, RIGHT?

39:02.078 --> 39:03.166
YEP.

39:03.166 --> 39:04.385
[both slurping]

39:06.126 --> 39:06.909
MR. JANE?

39:06.909 --> 39:08.433
MS. MONTAGUE.

39:08.433 --> 39:10.739
WE HAVE SOME IMPORTANT BUSINESS
TO CONCLUDE.

39:10.739 --> 39:12.306
WE DO?

39:16.397 --> 39:17.659
FOR YOU.

39:17.659 --> 39:20.270
AH.I--

39:20.270 --> 39:22.664
HANG ON.[chuckles]

39:22.664 --> 39:25.101
MM-HMM.
YEAH, THAT'S GOOD.

39:25.101 --> 39:27.103
OKAY?THANK YOU.

39:27.103 --> 39:29.105
I ALWAYS SETTLE MY DEBTS.

39:29.105 --> 39:32.239
YOU WERE RIGHT.
THAT WASN'T A SERIAL KILLER.

39:32.239 --> 39:35.808
MM. YOU REMIND ME.
I ALMOST FORGOT.

39:35.808 --> 39:38.288
THANK YOU.
FORGOTTEN IT, TOO.

39:38.288 --> 39:40.552
USEFUL BROOCH. UM, AND I--

39:40.552 --> 39:43.163
I WAS HOPING THAT, YOU KNOW,
YOU MIGHT FORGIVE ME

39:43.163 --> 39:45.208
ANY MISDIRECTION
I MIGHT HAVE GIVEN YOU.

39:45.208 --> 39:46.601
OH, YES. NO.

39:46.601 --> 39:50.257
NO, I-I...
ACTUALLY, IT WAS BRACING

39:50.257 --> 39:52.781
TO HAVE ONE'S
OPERATING PRINCIPLES CHALLENGED

39:52.781 --> 39:54.348
SO... ROBUSTLY.

39:54.348 --> 39:56.394
GLAD TO BE OF SERVICE.

39:56.394 --> 39:58.613
YOU KNOW,
I'VE NEVER PARTICIPATED

39:58.613 --> 40:00.267
IN CHICANERY BEFORE.

40:00.267 --> 40:02.269
I CAN'T CONDONE IT
AS A SYSTEM,

40:02.269 --> 40:05.315
BUT I MUST ADMIT THAT IT ADDS...
ZEST TO THE TASK AT HAND.

40:05.315 --> 40:06.360
[chuckles]

40:06.360 --> 40:08.449
IN FACT, W--

40:12.888 --> 40:17.197
HOW DID YOU FIGURE IT OUT,
THAT IT WAS ESTHER AND NILDA?

40:19.504 --> 40:21.331
JUST A GOOD GUESS.

40:21.331 --> 40:23.421
WHEN WE FIRST WITH THEM,

40:23.421 --> 40:27.642
THEY WERE MASKING SHAME,
NOT SADNESS.

40:27.642 --> 40:30.340
AND WHO LIKES LIZARDS?
COLD-BLOODED PEOPLE.

40:30.340 --> 40:31.733
LIZARDS.

40:31.733 --> 40:34.388
I THINK I SHALL STICK
WITH HARD NUMBERS.

40:34.388 --> 40:36.390
I HAVE ANOTHER GUESS
FOR YOU.

40:36.390 --> 40:38.348
THE CAVEMAN ISN'T
COMING BACK.

40:38.348 --> 40:40.481
HE IS ALMOST CERTAINLY DEAD.

40:40.481 --> 40:43.571
POSSIBLY. I HAVE NO
PERSONAL BIAS ON THE MATTER.

40:43.571 --> 40:46.661
THE NUMBERS WILL EVENTUALLY
REVEAL THE TRUTH EITHER WAY.

40:46.661 --> 40:48.228
THEY ALWAYS DO.

40:48.228 --> 40:49.708
YOU REALLY BELIEVE THAT?

40:49.708 --> 40:52.319
OF COURSE. IF YOU COULD
STAND FAR ENOUGH BACK

40:52.319 --> 40:56.802
TO SEE THE BIG PICTURE,
EVERYTHING IS NUMBERS.

40:56.802 --> 40:58.543
SPEAKING OF WHICH...

40:58.543 --> 41:01.502
YOU GAVE ME A GIFT,
SO I MUST GIVE YOU ONE.

41:01.502 --> 41:04.853
I RAN RED JOHN
THROUGH THE MODELING PROGRAM.

41:04.853 --> 41:07.682
YOU MIGHT FIND SOME
OF THE DATA SETS USEFUL.

41:07.682 --> 41:12.731
HMM. WOW. LOT OF FIGURES
AND GRAPHS HERE.

41:12.731 --> 41:14.123
THAT'S RIGHT.

41:14.123 --> 41:15.211
HMM.

41:19.389 --> 41:21.304
GOOD LUCK.

41:22.741 --> 41:24.220
WELL, THANK YOU.

41:29.269 --> 41:31.010
[thud]

41:41.716 --> 41:43.239
[dish clatters]

41:45.328 --> 41:46.721
[folder scrapes can]

41:46.721 --> 41:48.027
[lid clatters]

41:55.817 --> 41:58.559
STAY TUNED FOR SCENES
FROM OUR NEXT EPISODE.
